{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":61827,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"赞同","timestamp":1593408234,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61831,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"你清人会讨论？","timestamp":1593408258,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61832,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"你清人会讨论？","timestamp":1593408285,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61836,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不分区的必然后果，你把全清华的人拉到一块来聊天，吵架多正常……","timestamp":1593408303,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61837,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不好（狗头","timestamp":1593408307,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61838,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"对线我觉得是正常、合理的啊，不合理的是谩骂和阴阳怪气，通过说理进行对线有何不可","timestamp":1593408344,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61848,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 同意。阴阳怪气不少","timestamp":1593408387,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61858,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 啊，我说的对线就是毫无根据的抨击","timestamp":1593408431,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61872,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 原来对线是一个贬义词吗…我一直以为对线是指双方轮流发言形式的讨论","timestamp":1593408568,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61874,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 你们有没有想过，有些根源性的问题是不能白纸黑字地讨论，只能来回拐弯抹角呢？","timestamp":1593408582,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61880,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Hans: 树洞这样的洞很少吧…我就见过一个某人在疫情期间言论的洞是这样的，其他洞都应该不在这个范围内","timestamp":1593408625,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61896,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 我也不知道恰不恰当。比如我作为一个思想比较保守的人，确实不认同开放关系，但看到一些洞下面一些人上来就骂，就觉得挺难受的","timestamp":1593408713,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61901,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Hans: 因为大家不是真的蠢，有的人清楚地知道有些事是不对的，但是可以凭借一些表明的“证据”来麻痹自己和别人，享受其中的乐趣。你看那些聊开放性关系的人有几个能严格论证合理性的？","timestamp":1593408754,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61902,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 啥…我看着是反的，我觉得洞主需要带头有逻辑输出，而不是“就我…吗，不会吧不会吧”","timestamp":1593408761,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61928,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 确实，yygq和辱骂都不可取。就现在这状况感觉吓得好多想正常讨论的人都不敢发言了","timestamp":1593408863,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61960,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":10588,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"每个人的认知结构里都有一个红线画出的边界，超出那部分的是无法理解的，无法用已知逻辑合理化的，自然也不存在讨论的空间","timestamp":1593409061,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":3,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":10588,"reply":16,"tag":null,"text":"为啥很多洞本来应该和平地讨论问题，最后却演变成了各种对线呢？对于不认同的观点，相互尊重一下不好吗","timestamp":1593408201,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782585,"url":"","vote":{}}}